          "number": 7,
          "slidetitle": "Staying Safe With AI Equipment",
          "subtitle": "Practical steps to protect yourself daily",
          "slidecontent": "• Always read the operator manual before working alongside any AI-assisted machine\n• Check that sensors and cameras are clean and unobstructed at the start of each shift\n• Stay visible\n• Never assume the system has detected you, confirm it has\n• Report unusual machine behaviour to your supervisor immediately, even if the job seems urgent\n• Keep bystanders and colleagues well clear of autonomous equipment operating zones"
