        {
          "number": 8,
          "slidetitle": "What to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Essential points to carry with you",
          "slidecontent": "• AI in heavy machinery can act faster than any human can react, making pre-checks critical\n• Always verify sensor data manually before trusting an automated decision\n• Autonomous equipment still needs a trained human nearby\n• Know your override controls before the machine moves\n• Report every near-miss, even if the system \"corrected itself\"\n• Start small, one automated feature at a time, until you understand how it behaves in your conditions"
